const salaryFilter = [
  { message: 'Up to 400£ per day', type:'C', lowerLimit: 0, upperLimit: 400},
  { message: '400£ - 500£ per day', type:'C', lowerLimit: 400, upperLimit: 500 },
  { message: '500£ - 600£ per day', type:'C', lowerLimit: 500, upperLimit: 600 },
  { message: 'Over 600£ per day', type:'C', lowerLimit: 600, upperLimit: undefined },
  { message: 'Under 35000£ monthly', type:'P', lowerLimit: 0, upperLimit: 35000 },
  { message: '35000£ - 50000£ monthly', type:'P', lowerLimit: 35000, upperLimit: 50000 },
  { message: '50000£ - 75000£ monthly', type:'P', lowerLimit: 50000, upperLimit: 75000 },
  { message: '75000£ - 100000£ monthly', type:'P', lowerLimit: 75000, upperLimit: 100000 },
  { message: '100000£ - 150000£ monthly', type:'P', lowerLimit: 100000, upperLimit: 150000 },
  { message: 'Over 150000£ monthly', type:'P', lowerLimit: 150000, upperLimit: undefined },
];

export default salaryFilter;
